          <p>The inspiration for Ardtweeno came from the desire to retrieve and store data from my Arduino Mega 1280 prototyping board over a network. I attempted to develop a simple
		  solution using the Ethernet Shield with little success. Further research lead me to XBee radios and the serial interface they offer. It seemed like the perfect interface for my needs.
		  With a few hours development I created the prototype which later grew with the addition of new features to become Ardtweeno.</p>
